lead_paragraph: A'ja Wilson scored 27 points and Tiffany Mitchell added 20 as No. 2 South Carolina stayed unbeaten by holding on for a 70-63 victory over No. 10 Texas A&M on Sunday night.

headline.print_headline: Wilson's 27 Points Lifts No. 2 South Carolina Over Texas A&M
